\&\f(CW\*(C`x = u_1^{x_1}...u_r^{x_r}.\*(C'\fR\fIzeta\fR\f(CW\*(C`^{x_{r+1}}\*(C'\fR. The \f(CW\*(C`x_i\*(C'\fR are integers for
