.PP
\&\f(CW\*(C`v[6]\*(C'\fR is a copy of \f(CW\*(C`S\*(C'\fR.
.PP
The library syntax is \fBbnfsunit\fR\f(CW\*(C`(\*(C'\fR\fIbnf\fR\f(CW\*(C`,S,\*(C'\fR\fIprec\fR\f(CW\*(C`)\*(C'\fR.
.IX Xref "bnfsunit"
.ie n .SS "bnfunit""(""\fIbnf\fP"")"""
