if \fIchi\fR\f(CW\*(C` = \*(C'\fR\fIchi\fR is a (not necessarily primitive)
character over \fIbnr\fR, let
\&\f(CW\*(C`L(s,\*(C'\fR\fIchi\fR\f(CW\*(C`) = \*(C'\fR\fIsum\fR\f(CW\*(C`_{id} \*(C'\fR\fIchi\fR\f(CW\*(C`(id) N(id)^{\-s}\*(C'\fR be the associated
Artin L\-function. Returns the so-called Artin root number, i.e.\ the
complex number \f(CW\*(C`W(\*(C'\fR\fIchi\fR\f(CW\*(C`)\*(C'\fR of modulus 1 such that
.IX Xref "character Artin L-function Artin root number"
.PP
\&\ \ \fILambda\fR\f(CW\*(C`(1\-s,\*(C'\fR\fIchi\fR\f(CW\*(C`) = W(\*(C'\fR\fIchi\fR\f(CW\*(C`) \*(C'\fR\fILambda\fR\f(CW\*(C`(s,\eoverline{\*(C'\fR\fIchi\fR\f(CW\*(C`})\*(C'\fR
.PP
where \fILambda\fR\f(CW\*(C`(s,\*(C'\fR\fIchi\fR\f(CW\*(C`) = A(\*(C'\fR\fIchi\fR\f(CW\*(C`)^{s/2}\*(C'\fR\fIgamma\fR\f(CW\*(C`_\*(C'\fR\fIchi\fR\f(CW\*(C`(s) L(s,\*(C'\fR\fIchi\fR\f(CW\*(C`)\*(C'\fR is
