such that \fIchi\fR\f(CW\*(C`(g) = \*(C'\fR\fIzeta\fR\f(CW\*(C`^5\*(C'\fR, where \f(CW\*(C`g\*(C'\fR is the generator of the ray-class
field and \fIzeta\fR\f(CW\*(C` = e^{2i\*(C'\fR\fIPi\fR\f(CW\*(C`/N}\*(C'\fR where \f(CW\*(C`N\*(C'\fR is the order of \f(CW\*(C`g\*(C'\fR (\f(CW\*(C`N = 12\*(C'\fR as
