.IX Subsection "rnfpseudobasis(nf,pol)"
given a number field
\&\fInf\fR as output by \f(CW\*(C`nfinit\*(C'\fR and a polynomial \fIpol\fR with
coefficients in \fInf\fR defining a relative extension \f(CW\*(C`L\*(C'\fR of \fInf\fR,
computes a pseudo-basis \f(CW\*(C`(A,I)\*(C'\fR and the relative discriminant of \f(CW\*(C`L\*(C'\fR.
