.IX Xref "rnfsteinitz"
.IX Subsection "rnfsteinitz(nf,x)"
given a number field \fInf\fR as
output by \f(CW\*(C`nfinit\*(C'\fR and either a polynomial \f(CW\*(C`x\*(C'\fR with coefficients in
\&\fInf\fR defining a relative extension \f(CW\*(C`L\*(C'\fR of \fInf\fR, or a pseudo-basis
