\&\f(CW\*(C`x\*(C'\fR being an \f(CW\*(C`m x n\*(C'\fR matrix with \f(CW\*(C`m >= n\*(C'\fR
with rational or integer entries, this function has varying behaviour
depending on the sign of \f(CW\*(C`p\*(C'\fR:
.PP
