the second being the maximum norm found, and the last vector is a matrix
whose columns are the vectors found, only one being given for each
pair \f(CW\*(C`\f(CI+\-\f(CW v\*(C'\fR (at most \f(CW\*(C`m\*(C'\fR such pairs).
.PP
