(\fIflag\fR\f(CW\*(C` = 0\*(C'\fR),  \fBminim2\fR\f(CW\*(C`(x,b,m)\*(C'\fR (\fIflag\fR\f(CW\*(C` = 1\*(C'\fR), and finally
 \fBfincke_pohst\fR\f(CW\*(C`(x,b,m,\*(C'\fR\fIprec\fR\f(CW\*(C`)\*(C'\fR (\fIflag\fR\f(CW\*(C` = 2\*(C'\fR).
